stars = reviews %>% group_by(stars) %>% count(word,sort=T)

stars %>% 
  filter(n < 200 & n > 150) %>%
  mutate(word = reorder(word, n)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(word, n)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity") +
  xlab(NULL) +
  coord_flip() + facet_wrap(~stars)
